<hw>Frappe</hw></mhw>
<pr>(fr⟦adot⟧`p⟦amac⟧")</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[F., p.p. of
<ets>frapper</ets> to strike, to chill.]</ety> <def>Iced; frozen;
